ng services. It serves multi-national companies, other corporates, retailers, bulk consumers, original equipment manufacturers, government departments, households, philanthropic organizations, educational institutions, and various other entities. The company was formerly known as Infotrek Syscom Limited and changed its name to Eco Recycling Limited in December 2010. Eco Recycling Limited was incorporated in 1994 and is based in Mumbai, India. Eco Recycling Limited is a subsidiary of Ecoreco Ventures Private Limited."}}